# MAINCORE 2: CONTEXT CHO TAI LIEU ERD + FLOWCHART

Tai lieu nay la context chuyen dung de tao:
1) DATABASE ERD
2) So do luong nghiep vu (flowchart)

Muc tieu: tai lieu hoa he thong theo goc nhin System Design, khong sa vao chi tiet code UI.

## 1. SCOPE TAI LIEU
- Pham vi backend nghiep vu core cua PCS + smart parking layout.
- Uu tien flow: check-in, check-out, dashboard-summary, active-sessions, parking-layout, slot-suggestion.
- Co bao gom idempotency va race-condition handling o muc logic he thong.
- Khong mo rong sang microservice/distributed architecture o giai doan nay.

## 2. DATABASE ERD CONTEXT

### 2.1 Bang cot loi can co trong ERD
1. `users`
   - id (PK, UUID)
   - username
   - password_hash
   - role (`ADMIN`, `GUARD`)
   - is_deleted

2. `vehicles`
   - id (PK, UUID)
   - license_plate (UNIQUE)
   - vehicle_type (enum nghiep vu da chuan hoa)
   - is_deleted

3. `monthly_tickets`
   - id (PK, UUID)
   - vehicle_id (FK -> vehicles.id)
   - customer_name
   - expiration_date
   - is_deleted

4. `pricing_config`
   - id (PK, UUID)
   - vehicle_type (UNIQUE theo nghiep vu)
   - free_minutes
   - day_rate
   - night_rate
   - max_daily_fee

5. `parking_sessions`
   - id (PK, UUID)
   - vehicle_id (FK -> vehicles.id)
   - guard_in_id (FK -> users.id)
   - guard_out_id (FK -> users.id, nullable)
   - monthly_ticket_id (FK -> monthly_tickets.id, nullable)
   - slot_id (FK -> parking_slots.id, nullable)
   - time_in
   - time_out (nullable)
   - total_fee (nullable truoc check-out)
   - exception_type (nullable, vd `LOST_TICKET`)
   - note (nullable)
   - is_deleted

6. `parking_areas`
   - id (PK, UUID)
   - code (UNIQUE, vd `A`, `B`, `C`)
   - name
   - is_active
   - is_deleted

7. `parking_slots`
   - id (PK, UUID)
   - area_id (FK -> parking_areas.id)
   - slot_code (UNIQUE, vd `A01`, `B03`)
   - supported_vehicle_type (nullable, null = all)
   - status (`FREE`, `OCCUPIED`, `MAINTENANCE`)
   - is_active
   - is_deleted

8. `api_idempotency`
   - endpoint
   - idempotency_key
   - is_completed
   - status_code
   - response_payload
   - created_at
   - expires_at
   - unique key: (endpoint, idempotency_key)

9. `monthly_ticket_renewals`
   - id (PK, UUID)
   - monthly_ticket_id (FK -> monthly_tickets.id)
   - old_expiration_date
   - new_expiration_date
   - note (nullable)
   - changed_at

### 2.2 Quan he can the hien tren ERD
- `vehicles (1) -> (N) parking_sessions`
- `users (1) -> (N) parking_sessions` qua `guard_in_id`
- `users (1) -> (N) parking_sessions` qua `guard_out_id`
- `vehicles (1) -> (N) monthly_tickets`
- `monthly_tickets (0..1) -> (N) parking_sessions` (optional gan vao session check-in)
- `parking_areas (1) -> (N) parking_slots`
- `parking_slots (1) -> (N) parking_sessions` qua `slot_id`
- `monthly_tickets (1) -> (N) monthly_ticket_renewals`
- `pricing_config` tham chieu logic theo `vehicle_type` (logical relation, khong bat buoc FK)

### 2.3 Invariants/Rang buoc bat buoc ghi chu tren ERD
- Mot xe chi co toi da 1 session dang mo (`time_out IS NULL`) tai moi thoi diem.
- `vehicles.vehicle_type` chi nhan tap gia tri nghiep vu hop le.
- `parking_slots.status` chi nhan `FREE`, `OCCUPIED`, `MAINTENANCE`.
- Khong duoc dat `MAINTENANCE` cho slot dang `OCCUPIED`.
- Khi transfer slot thanh cong: slot cu -> `FREE`, slot moi -> `OCCUPIED` trong cung transaction.
- `api_idempotency` dam bao duplicate submit khong tao tac vu trung.
- Soft-delete duoc su dung o cac bang nghiep vu (`is_deleted`).

## 3. BUSINESS FLOWCHART CONTEXT

### 3.1 Flowchart 01 - Check-in
Buoc bat buoc:
1. Nhan request check-in (license_plate, vehicle_type, guard_in_id, idempotency-key)
2. Validate input + normalize vehicle_type
3. Kiem tra idempotency:
   - neu da completed -> replay response
   - neu in-progress -> bao conflict/phu hop policy
4. Bat dau transaction
5. Tim vehicle theo license_plate
6. Neu chua co vehicle -> tao vehicle moi
7. Kiem tra session dang mo:
   - neu co -> rollback + 409
8. Kiem tra ve thang con han (neu co)
9. Chon slot trong phu hop theo `vehicle_type` (`FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED`)
10. Reserve slot (`FREE -> OCCUPIED`)
11. Tao parking_session moi (time_in=NOW, monthly_ticket_id co the null, co `slot_id`)
12. Mark idempotency completed + luu response
13. Commit + tra ket qua (bao gom `slotCode`)
14. Neu loi o bat ky buoc nao -> rollback + rollback idempotency record dang mo

### 3.2 Flowchart 02 - Check-out
Buoc bat buoc:
1. Nhan request check-out (license_plate, guard_out_id, exception_type, note, idempotency-key)
2. Validate input
3. Kiem tra idempotency:
   - neu da completed -> replay response
   - neu in-progress -> conflict/phu hop policy
4. Bat dau transaction
5. Tim session dang mo cua xe + lock row (`FOR UPDATE`)
6. Neu khong tim thay -> rollback + 404
7. Re-check nghiep vu:
   - neu `LOST_TICKET` -> tinh phi theo policy phat
   - neu binh thuong -> tinh phi qua pricingService + pricing_config
8. Update session (time_out, guard_out_id, total_fee, exception_type, note)
9. Giai phong slot cua session (`OCCUPIED -> FREE`)
10. Mark idempotency completed + luu response
11. Commit + tra invoice
12. Neu loi -> rollback + rollback idempotency dang mo

### 3.3 Flowchart 03 - Dashboard Summary
1. Nhan request
2. Truy van aggregate:
   - vehicles_in_lot
   - check_ins_today
   - check_outs_today
   - revenue_today
   - hourly_revenue
3. Tra response tong hop
4. Neu loi -> tra message ro rang + status phu hop

### 3.4 Flowchart 04 - Active Sessions
1. Nhan request
2. Lay danh sach session dang mo (time_out IS NULL) + thong tin vehicle + `slot_code`
3. Sort theo time_in giam dan (backend hien tai), UI co the sap xep lai theo muc uu tien van hanh
4. Tra response de UI render queue van hanh

### 3.5 Flowchart 05 - Parking Layout
1. Nhan request `GET /api/parking-layout`
2. Join `parking_areas` + `parking_slots` + active `parking_sessions`
3. Group theo area
4. Tinh summary moi khu (`total_slots`, `occupied_slots`, `free_slots`)
5. Tra response cho UI so do bai

### 3.6 Flowchart 06 - Slot Suggestion
1. Nhan request `GET /api/slot-suggestion?vehicle_type=...`
2. Neu thieu `vehicle_type` -> tra message huong dan
3. Tim slot FREE dau tien phu hop loai xe
4. Tinh fill-rate tung khu + tao alerts cho khu `>=85%`
5. Tra response gom `suggestion`, `alerts`, `message`

### 3.7 Flowchart 07 - Slot Maintenance (Lock/Unlock)
1. Nhan request `PUT /api/slots/:slot_code/maintenance` voi `is_maintenance`
2. Lock row slot theo `slot_code`
3. Validate nghiep vu:
   - Neu slot dang `OCCUPIED` -> khong cho lock/unlock trai phep
4. Update status:
   - `is_maintenance=true` -> `MAINTENANCE`
   - `is_maintenance=false` -> `FREE`
5. Commit + tra ket qua

### 3.8 Flowchart 08 - Transfer Active Session Slot
1. Nhan request `PUT /api/sessions/transfer-slot` (license_plate, target_slot_code)
2. Tim session dang mo cua xe + lock session
3. Tim slot dich + lock slot dich
4. Validate:
   - slot dich phai `FREE`
   - slot dich phai phu hop `vehicle_type` (neu co constraint)
   - slot dich khong trung slot hien tai
5. Giai phong slot cu (`FREE`) neu co
6. Gan session vao slot moi + set slot moi `OCCUPIED`
7. Commit + tra ket qua from/to slot

### 3.9 Flowchart 09 - Monthly Ticket Renewal History
1. Gia han ve thang: `PUT /api/monthly-tickets/:license_plate/renew`
2. Validate ngay moi > ngay het han hien tai
3. Update `monthly_tickets.expiration_date`
4. Insert ban ghi vao `monthly_ticket_renewals`
5. Co endpoint `GET /api/monthly-tickets/:license_plate/renewals` de tra lich su

## 4. ERROR MATRIX CHO FLOWCHART
- 400: input invalid / vi pham contract
- 401/403: khong duoc phep truy cap
- 404: khong tim thay session/doi tuong can thao tac
- 409: xung dot du lieu (xe dang trong bai, race-condition, in-progress idempotent, het cho phu hop, slot khong hop le cho thao tac)
- 429: qua tan suat goi API
- 500: loi he thong/DB bat thuong

## 5. CAC DIEM PHAI GHI CHU KHI VE SO DO
- Ghi ro "transaction boundary" trong check-in/check-out.
- Danh dau cac decision node quan trong:
  - vehicle ton tai?
  - session dang mo ton tai?
  - slot trong phu hop con khong?
  - lost ticket?
  - idempotency replay?
- Danh dau "critical section" cua check-out (`FOR UPDATE`).
- Danh dau "consistency guarantee": one active session per vehicle.
- Danh dau "slot lifecycle": `FREE -> OCCUPIED -> FREE`.
- Danh dau "maintenance lifecycle": `FREE <-> MAINTENANCE` (khong di truc tiep tu `OCCUPIED`).

